<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 mò hòu de rì zi a, yé hé huá diàn de shān, bì jiān lì bì jiān lì, bì jiān lì.
 chāo hū zhū shān, gāo guò wàn wàn lǐng, wàn mín dōu yào liú guī tā de shān.
 shèng líng zhī huǒ zhèng zài rán shāo, zhǔ de jiù ēn jiāng yào chuán biàn.
 liú wáng de rén dōu yào huí xiāng, biān zǒu biān jiāo tán.
 wéi yǒu yé sū shì jiù ēn de quán yuán. tā yào gěi hēi àn de shí dài zhǎn xīn de gǎi biàn.
 lóng zi yào tīng jiàn, xiā zi yào kàn jiàn, wàn mín dōu yào liú guī zhǔ shèng shān.</lyrics>
<title>mò hòu de rì zi 迦南857</title>
<hymn_number>857</hymn_number>
